title: 'Star Wars' fans clamor for tickets, wonder where's Luke
text: 'Star Wars' fans clamor for tickets, wonder where's Luke Tuesday, 20 October 2015 (12 minutes ago) Millions of fans cried out in joy after they saw the latest trailer for " Star Wars : The Force Awakens," but it also left more than a few wondering where Luke Skywalker has been during all the marketing. Source: Wochit News - 23 hours ago Star Wars Fans Are Unhappy They Have to Watch Football to See New Force Awakens Trailer 00:56 Today Your source for all things celebrity and entertainment. Star Wars fans, did you hear? The new trailer for The Force Awakens is debuting tonight! Can you guess where? YouTube? Facebook? During a marathon of the Star Wars saga on ABC Family?
